name: The Street of Future Dreams #1
description: Digital modified art, out of one original painting made by us. Unique and highly collectible. With this one, I would like you to get it in your collections for free, as a sort of introduction into this NFT world, all new to me. Consider it as Limited Edition Print, as NFT is a sort of certificate like our signature. We are happy to share with you. So, edition 100 at 0 Tezos and 3 more which will be priced at 10 Tezos each, the current prize of our posters in many places. Enjoy and collect!. In classical markets, this work would cost you, LE Print handsigned by me Euro 200/500
